values.title: Cloaks+
values.description: Cloaks+ is a Minecraft cape service that allows users to customize their character's appearance further than ever before imagined. We utilize may different languages and technologies across our many services, all seamlessly linked together.

values.title: Komodo
values.description: Komodo is a custom programming language I am working on which is dynamically typed and suports multiple programming paradigms. It is interpretted by a completely custom interpreter written in java and kotlin which does not use any third party lexing libraries.

values.title: Cards Against Humanity Online
values.description: Inspired by several existing online ports of the game, I decided to make my own that looks and feels much nicer than existing versions.

values.title: Node Resemble
values.description: Updated javascript image similarity library with added support for async await functionality. (No dependence on canvas so can be used anywhere)
